Post.title: Ubuntu for Win10 K3 syncdial
Post._content:
K3LEDEsyncdial()
![,MMP](lede-k3-compile-syncdial/1516378730321.png)

LinuxUbuntu for Win10  >  > Windows
`LinuxWindows`

## LEDE K3 SDK
> windows, ubuntu wget

openwrt[	openwrt.proxy.ustclug.org](	openwrt.proxy.ustclug.org)
SDK:[lede-sdk-17.01.4-bcm53xx_gcc-5.4.0_musl-1.1.16_eabi.Linux-x86_64](http://openwrt.proxy.ustclug.org/releases/17.01.4/targets/bcm53xx/generic/lede-sdk-17.01.4-bcm53xx_gcc-5.4.0_musl-1.1.16_eabi.Linux-x86_64.tar.xz)
```bash
# Dlede
cd /mnt/d/ && mkdir lede
#SDK
wget http://openwrt.proxy.ustclug.org/releases/17.01.4/targets/bcm53xx/generic/lede-sdk-17.01.4-bcm53xx_gcc-5.4.0_musl-1.1.16_eabi.Linux-x86_64.tar.xz
# SDK lede-sdk
tar xvJf lede-sdk-17.01.4-bcm53xx_gcc-5.4.0_musl-1.1.16_eabi.Linux-x86_64.tar.xz -C lede-sdk
# sdk
cd lede-sdk
# 
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install build-essential asciidoc binutils bzip2 gawk gettext git libncurses5-dev libz-dev patch unzip zlib1g-dev lib32gcc1 libc6-dev-i386 subversion flex uglifyjs git-core gcc-multilib p7zip p7zip-full msmtp libssl-dev texinfo libglib2.0-dev
```

package

: https://pan.baidu.com/s/1pMPhJ5L : fu6r

## luci-app-syncdial

```bash
make menuconfig
#  Luci > Application > luci-app-syncdial
# 
make package/luci-app-syncdial/compile V=99
```
`bin`

## 
winscp
```bash
opkg install luci-app-syncdial_2.0-22_all.ipk
```

Post.title: HTTPS SSL
Post._content:
# 
```bash
#
openssl x509 -in cert.crt -text -noout

#DER encoded
openssl x509 -in uhttpd.crt -inform der -text -noout

#PEM to DER
openssl x509 -in cert.crt -outform der -out uhttpd.crt
openssl rsa -in cert.key -outform der -out uhttpd.key

#DER to PEM
openssl x509 -in uhttpd.crt -inform der -outform pem -out cert.crt
openssl rsa -in uhttpd.key -inform der -outform pem -out cert.key
```
